---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | SF Travels - Redefining Premium Mobility in Bangalore"
  description="Learn about the legacy of SF Travels. Built on absolute safety, transparent slab rate pricing, exceptional chauffeur hospitality, and executive corporate fleet transport."
>
  
  <main class="bg-white min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden pt-12 text-slate-800">
    <!-- Hero Banner Section (Matches homepage dark-themed vibe, styled for bright and clear readability) -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0"
            style="background-image: url('https://horizons-cdn.hostinger.com/e3da7081-89fa-4296-8e0b-208ae94398b5/bda0fdb8b258bf205c0653b2583c1ec0.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: fixed;">
        </div>
        <!-- Ultra-premium high-contrast dark overlay to make text pop -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#050914]/95 via-[#0A1128]/85 to-[#050914]/95 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-20 text-center max-w-4xl">
            <span class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] block mb-4 drop-shadow" style="color: #ffffff !important;">ABOUT SF Travels</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight drop-shadow-md" style="color: #ffffff !important;">
                Redefining Premium Mobility <br /><span style="color: #fbbf24 !important;" class="drop-shadow-md">in Bangalore</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed font-semibold drop-shadow-md" style="color: #ffffff !important;">
                Learn about the legacy of SF Travels. Built on absolute safety, transparent slab rate pricing, exceptional chauffeur hospitality, and executive corporate fleet transport.
            </p>
            <div class="inline-block bg-[#D97706]/20 border border-[#D97706]/40 text-[#fbbf24] font-bold text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full shadow-md backdrop-blur-sm">
                <span>"Smooth Ride On Time"</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Story Section (Matches homepage's grid with floating cards) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-16">
                <!-- Left: Copy -->
                <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                    <span class="text-[#D97706] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-3 block">Who We Are</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] mb-6">Our Story</h2>
                    <div class="prose prose-lg text-slate-600 space-y-5 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>SF Travels has been serving Bangalore with premium taxi and vehicle rental
                            services. What started as a small venture has grown into one of the most trusted
                            transportation service providers in the city, thanks to our commitment to quality and
                            customer satisfaction.</p>
                        <p>We understand that transportation is more than just getting from point A to point B. It's
                            about comfort, safety, reliability, and peace of mind. That's why we've built our business
                            on these core principles, ensuring every journey with us is a pleasant experience.</p>
                        <p>Today, we serve thousands of satisfied customers ranging from individual travelers to
                            corporate clients, providing everything from airport transfers to outstation trips, local
                            rentals to event transportation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Right: Image with overlaps -->
                <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full relative">
                    <!-- Floating shadow background glow -->
                    <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#D97706]/15 to-[#1E2D5A]/10 rounded-[36px] blur-2xl opacity-60"></div>
                    <div class="relative group px-4">
                        <div class="absolute -inset-2 bg-[#1E2D5A]/10 rounded-2xl transform rotate-3 -z-10 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-6"></div>
                        <img
                            src="/premium_travel_fleet.png"
                            alt="SF Travels Premium Fleet"
                            class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-2xl object-cover transform transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-[1.01]"
                        />
                        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-2 bg-slate-900/95 backdrop-blur-md p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-800 hidden md:flex items-center gap-4 text-white z-20">
                            <div class="bg-[#D97706]/15 p-3 rounded-xl border border-[#D97706]/30">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                    width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#D97706"
                                    stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    class="w-6 h-6">
                                    <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"></circle>
                                    <path d="M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest">Experience</p>
                                <p class="text-base font-extrabold text-[#D97706]">Premium Quality Service</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission & Vision Section (Alternating layout: Car Image on Left, Cards on Right) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#fafaf8] border-y border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-96 h-96 bg-[#1E2D5A]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 bg-[#D97706]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-16">
                <!-- Left: Luxury Car Image -->
                <div class="lg:w-5/12 w-full relative">
                    <!-- Floating shadow background glow -->
                    <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#D97706]/10 to-[#1E2D5A]/15 rounded-[36px] blur-2xl opacity-60"></div>
                    <div class="relative group px-4">
                        <div class="absolute -inset-2 bg-[#D97706]/10 rounded-2xl transform -rotate-3 -z-10 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:-rotate-6"></div>
                        <img
                            src="/luxury_mission_car.png"
                            alt="SF Travels Premium Sedan"
                            class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-2xl object-cover transform transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-[1.01]"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Right: Mission & Vision Cards Stack -->
                <div class="lg:w-7/12 w-full flex flex-col gap-8">
                    <!-- Mission Card -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 border-t-8 border-t-[#1E2D5A] hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.01] transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#1E2D5A]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#1E2D5A" stroke-width="2.5" class="w-6 h-6">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            To provide safe, reliable, and comfortable transportation services that exceed customer expectations. We strive to make every journey pleasant and hassle-free by maintaining the highest standards of service quality and professionalism.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Vision Card -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 border-t-8 border-t-[#D97706] hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.01] transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2.5" class="w-6 h-6">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            To be the most preferred transportation service provider in Bangalore and beyond, known for our commitment to excellence, innovation, and customer satisfaction. We aim to set new benchmarks in the travel and tourism industry.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Values Section (Matches the homepage clean features section) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="text-[#D97706] font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] block text-center mb-3">Our Core Values</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] text-center mb-5">The Principles We Stand By</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed">We guide our daily operations through an unwavering commitment to integrity and quality travel.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                <!-- Value 1: Passenger Safety -->
                <div class="group rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 bg-[#fafaf8] hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl hover:border-slate-200/60 transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#1E2D5A]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#1E2D5A] transition-colors duration-300">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#1E2D5A] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1f36] mb-3 group-hover:text-[#1E2D5A] transition-colors">Passenger Safety</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Our fundamental pledge. We prioritize human lives above all, anchoring every operational policy in safety.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Value 2: Absolute Reliability -->
                <div class="group rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 bg-[#fafaf8] hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl hover:border-slate-200/60 transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#D97706] transition-colors duration-300">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#D97706] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1f36] mb-3 group-hover:text-[#D97706] transition-colors">Absolute Reliability</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Honoring our promises. We hold every booking as a strict commitment, ensuring on-time readiness.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Value 3: Empathy & Respect -->
                <div class="group rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 bg-[#fafaf8] hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl hover:border-slate-200/60 transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#1E2D5A]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#1E2D5A] transition-colors duration-300">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#1E2D5A] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1f36] mb-3 group-hover:text-[#1E2D5A] transition-colors">Empathy & Respect</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">We treat passengers, employees, and driver partners with dignity, fostering genuine hospitality.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Value 4: Honesty & Transparency -->
                <div class="group rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 bg-[#fafaf8] hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl hover:border-slate-200/60 transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#D97706] transition-colors duration-300">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#D97706] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v17M12 20H8m4 0h4M3 10h18M6 10l-2 6h4l-2-6zm12 0l-2 6h4l-2-6z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1f36] mb-3 group-hover:text-[#D97706] transition-colors">Honesty & Transparency</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">No hidden agendas. We commit to upfront pricing and truthful, transparent communication.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Us Section (Matches the homepage's News/Stories and clean 3-col grids) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#f5f4f0] border-t border-slate-100">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="text-[#D97706] font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] block mb-3">Why Choose Us</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] mb-5">Everything You Expect from a Premium Travel Partner</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed">We provide Bangalore's most reliable and professional executive passenger transit.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-7">
                <!-- Reason 1: Diverse Fleet Selection -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-[#D97706]">
                            <path d="M19 17h2c.6 0 1-.4 1-1v-3c0-.9-.7-1.7-1.5-1.9C18.7 10.6 16 10 16 10s-1.3-1.4-2.2-2.3c-.5-.4-1.1-.7-1.8-.7H5c-.6 0-1.1.4-1.4.9l-1.4 2.9A3.7 3.7 0 0 0 2 12v4c0 .6.4 1 1 1h2"></path>
                            <circle cx="7" cy="17" r="2"></circle>
                            <path d="M9 17h6"></path>
                            <circle cx="17" cy="17" r="2"></circle>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] text-lg mb-2">Diverse Fleet Selection</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">From executive sedans and premium SUVs (Innova Crysta, Hycross) to luxury vans, we offer a wide range of vehicles for every travel requirement.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Reason 2: Chauffeur Etiquette & Skill -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-[#D97706]">
                            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                            <path d="m22 10-6 6-2-2"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] text-lg mb-2">Chauffeur Etiquette & Skill</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">Background-verified drivers trained in corporate protocols, safety guidelines, and optimal route navigation across Bangalore.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Reason 3: 24/7 Operations Desk -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-[#D97706]">
                            <path d="M3 18v-6a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v6"></path>
                            <path d="M21 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3zM3 19a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h1a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H3z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] text-lg mb-2">24/7 Operations Desk</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">Round-the-clock dispatchers monitoring flight statuses, live traffic feeds, and managing adjustments in real-time.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Reason 4: No-Surge Slab Rates -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-[#D97706]">
                            <path d="M12 2H2v10l9.29 9.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.41 0l7.29-7.29a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.41L12 2z"></path>
                            <line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"></line>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] text-lg mb-2">No-Surge Slab Rates</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">Enjoy predictable pricing with defined mileage slabs. Zero peak-hour surge multipliers or hidden administrative fees.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Reason 5: Live GPS & Journey Tracking -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-[#D97706]">
                            <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
                            <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] text-lg mb-2">Live GPS Tracking</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">Complete route visibility with active GPS monitoring and real-time trip status alerts for enhanced safety.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Reason 6: Corporate-Grade Logistics -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200/50 hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-[#D97706]">
                            <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                            <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] text-lg mb-2">Corporate-Grade Logistics</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">Custom booking portals, priority dispatch desks, and structured B2B invoicing systems tailored for MNC corporate compliance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
